    Nighteyes looked to Squizzy, "Thanks...my leg, its killing me. I need a 
CR chamber right away...cough cough.." She said as mech, mixed with her 
siliva splattered on the doorstep.

    Aracnia sipped her glass from the toast, stood up, and followed her 
escourt out. "I think this meeting was a success. Together, the Predacons 
will dominate this rock." She said, and giggled.

    Megatron and Hell Beast both leaned closer t othe screen tring to get a 
better look at what they were reciving. The picture was blurry, and on top of 
that what ever it was looking at was to dark to make out.
    "This had better work, Megatron, if we get caught-" Hell Beast said in a 
displeased tone. He wasnt very perceptive to this newest scheme, and the risk 
was high.
    "-It will work! And if it dosent then we can abort. No harm will come to 
us, yesss." He said with a big dumb smile on his face. It was his dea, nad he 
was going to follow it through, even if Hell Beast didnt like it.
